      <h3>Loadout &amp; Comp Presets</h3>
      <p class="muted">Quick guidance for weapon splits. Adjust to enemy comp and map size.</p>
      <table>
        <tr><th>Preset</th><th>When to Use</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
        <tr><td>Default: 2 AR / 2 SMG</td><td>Balanced maps and most Hardpoints</td><td>Anchor AR, Flex AR, SMG Slayer, SMG Support</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Aggro: 1 AR / 3 SMG</td><td>Small/CQB maps; when losing close fights</td><td>Flex swaps to SMG; emphasize trades &amp; stuns</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Lockdown: 3 AR / 1 SMG</td><td>Open maps; Control defense; winning long lanes</td><td>Flex to AR; SMG focuses info and pinches</td></tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>Anchor &amp; Support Cheat Sheet</h3>
      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <h4>Anchor ‚Äì Rules</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Live first, kill second. Your death flips maps.</li>
            <li>Call <strong>numbers + timing</strong> (e.g., ‚Äú2 long, 5s‚Äù) and ask for the <em>nearest help</em> (Flex).</li>
            <li>Rotate at -15s unless spawn block is contested.</li>
            <li>Don‚Äôt ego-chow power ARs; use off-angles.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Support ‚Äì Rules</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Be with someone always; your value is trades.</li>
            <li>Lead with utility (stuns/smokes); trophy down <em>before</em> you‚Äôre seen.</li>
            <li>Reset if 2 dead; don‚Äôt feed streaks.</li>
            <li>Own cutoffs on rotations; deny their reinforcements.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hr"></div>
      <h4>Micro-Call Templates</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><code>‚ÄúTwo my lane, 1 weak ‚Äî 3s out. Need Flex.‚Äù</code></li>
        <li><code>‚ÄúTrophy down. I‚Äôm first contact, trade me on 3.‚Äù</code></li>
        <li><code>‚ÄúSmoke out long AR. Pinch in 5, go.‚Äù</code></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

